Package jade.security

Interface JADEPrincipal

All Superinterfaces:
Principal
public interface JADEPrincipal extends Principal
The JADEPrincipal interface represents all principals acting on the platform. They will be held responsible for their own agents and containers.

    • getEncoded

      byte[] getEncoded()
      Checks the hierarchical relationship between two principals, i.e. tells if this principal belongs to group p . If this holds, all permissions granted to p will be automatically granted to this principal, too. param p The principal to check. return True if this principal is a member of group p .
